    <briefdescription>
<para>Linkable loadable extension loader context. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This object is used to access the ELF file data and cache its contents while an extension is being loaded by the LLEXT subsystem. Once the extension is loaded, this object is no longer needed. </para>
